I. copy dotfiles to /home/user directory.

II. pacstrap -k base /mnt/

III. launch chaotic-repo.sh

IV. restore arch_system_config_ddmmyy (made with root-backup.sh).

V. pacman -Syyu - < pkglist.txt

VI. Set root password: passwd root

VII. create non-privileged user:

useradd -m -G wheel,network,video,audio -s /usr/bin/zsh username

passwd username 

VIII. set localtime

ln -sf /usr/share/zoneinfo/Zone/SubZone /etc/localtime

IX. as user: dconf load / < dconf_settings_backup.txt

X. as user - launch setup.sh

XI. configure mullvad and create uefi boot entry
